room_title: Escape room "The Lucky Duck Speakeasy" by Xscape Our Rooms in St. Augustine
room_address: 197 Blackford Way, Suite B, Saint Augustine, FL 32086
room_description:
It is 1925 and prohibition is in full swing. You are part of a team initiating a crackdown on illegal sales and transportation of liquor. The evidence you need to identify the kingpin of the illegal activities is contained within the infamous Lucky Duck Speakeasy.
A bomb has been set to destroy the building and its secrets. You and your team have 60 minutes to find the evidence and escape. You have just 60 minutes to identify the Boss and diffuse the bomb before detonation!
